text:
This bug is to track a smallchange I've made on PCLRenderer.java to allow PCL
Renderer to autoselect portrait or landscape page mode.

PCL Renderer doesn't know anything about page modes, but we can made some
assumptions, so we can make thinks easier to FOP users...

Created attachment 1228
Sorry unwanted changes on previous patch. This is OK. v1.1
